title: 1.12安装更好的附魔台EnchantingPlus后游戏崩溃(已安装前置BookShelf)
author: zbw123y
txt_content:
本帖最后由 zbw123y 于 2020-3-25 22:48 编辑 

游戏安装了更好的附魔台，提示要安装2.3.557以上版本的BookShelf当前置文件，下载完前置文件以后，游戏崩溃附件文档为崩溃信息
在崩溃信息定位了一下，发现问题处在eplus上，也就是更好的附魔台mod,但是不知道该如何解决，恳请大佬们救助下我这个萌新
[url=]crash-2020-03-25_22.28.17-clie ...[/url]
以下为启动器的error和fatals信息
[22:28:01] [main/ERROR] [mixin]: Critical problem: mixins.liteloader.client.preinit.json:MixinClientBrandRetriever target net.minecraft.client.ClientBrandRetriever was already transformed.


[22:28:02] [main/WARN] [LaunchWrapper]: Tweak class name org.spongepowered.asm.mixin.EnvironmentStateTweaker has already been visited -- skipping


[22:28:11] [main/WARN]: Skipping bad option: lastServer:


[22:28:17] [main/FATAL] [FML]: Fatal errors were detected during the transition from CONSTRUCTING to PREINITIALIZATION. Loading cannot continue


[22:28:17] [main/FATAL] [FML]: 


[22:28:17] [main/FATAL] [FML]: The following problems were captured during this phase


[22:28:17] [main/ERROR] [FML]: Caught exception from eplus (java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: net/minecraftforge/client/event/ColorHandlerEvent$Block)
